## Common Mistakes to Avoid

‚ùå **Don't**:
- Mark task complete without testing
- Skip running checkpoints
- Work on multiple tasks at once
- Forget to commit your code
- Ignore acceptance criteria

‚úÖ **Do**:
- Test thoroughly
- Checkpoint regularly (every 30 min)
- Work sequentially
- Commit after each task
- Follow acceptance criteria

